cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.SI

The paper discusses OpenML, a platform for sharing and organizing data in machine learning research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of online tools for organizing and mining information, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the focus on data organization and sharing could also relate to cs.DB (Databases). The paper briefly mentions collaboration and visibility, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
